				<a href="https://cepr.org/publications/dp18383" class="text-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Man Bites Dog: Editorial Choices and Biases in the Reporting of Weather Events</a>
				</strong> - with
				<a class="cactus-link" href="https://nicolamastrorocco.com/" class="text-link hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nicola Mastrorocco</a>, 
